Interface TransactionType

Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface TransactionType
Represents a type of transaction that you can apply to an AbstractInventory.

  • Field Details

    • ADD

      static final TransactionType ADD
      Adds an item to the inventory. Can either take an air slot or be stacked.

    • TAKE

      static final TransactionType TAKE
      Takes an item from the inventory. Can either transform items to air or reduce their amount.
